index ac8f32acf9016bfc722753eb12db52568445a158..5b01c66d5cdc0b5fa6d40274aa130e699b777c29
--- a/docs/examples.rst
+++ b/docs/examples.rst
@@ -244,6 +244,16 @@
 
 The ``until`` method sets the jobs deadline. The job will not run after the deadline.
 
+Run a job a limited number of times
+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+
+.. code-block:: python
+
+    # Run my_job three times, then cancel it.
+    schedule.every(1).hours.max_runs(3).do(my_job)
+
+The ``max_runs`` method sets the maximum number of times a job will run.
+
 Time until the next execution
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 Use ``schedule.idle_seconds()`` to get the number of seconds until the next job is scheduled to run.
