   244	
   245	The ``until`` method sets the jobs deadline. The job will not run after the deadline.
   246	
   247	Run a job a limited number of times
   248	~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   249	
   250	.. code-block:: python
   251	
   252	    # Run my_job three times, then cancel it.
   253	    schedule.every(1).hours.max_runs(3).do(my_job)
   254	
   255	The ``max_runs`` method sets the maximum number of times a job will run.
   256	
   257	Time until the next execution
   258	~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   259	Use ``schedule.idle_seconds()`` to get the number of seconds until the next job is scheduled to run.
   260	The returned value is negative if the next scheduled jobs was scheduled to run in the past.
   261	Returns ``None`` if no jobs are scheduled.
   262	
